{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The United States had gone into isolation and gone dry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so really, we-- we were content.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were members of the Empire on which the sun never set and we all worked together and we all pulled together.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we used to have the Australian cricket team used to come to England and play cricket with us and they used to thrash us sometimes and sometimes we thrashed them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was all great fun and it was like going home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Wherever you went, you were going home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "18.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if there were, they kept it to themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure I would have remembered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, in those days we had horses, and horses pulled the guns and did everything else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the day started with horses-- feeding them, grooming them, washing them, watering them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All took time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you'd done all that, then you could go and have your breakfast.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you were slow eating your breakfast, then you were in the [INAUDIBLE] because you had to get on parade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you never stopped, never stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no windbreaks between sessions on the square or studying or in the gymnasium or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was pretty hard going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you were all volunteers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You'd all said, we'll do it and you were equally determined one way or another that you wouldn't let your mate down and your mate wouldn't let you down.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then after whatever it was, 14 weeks, you qualified.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Every Sunday you had to go to church.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the-- that was a great day for the Church of England, too, because we all used to have to go on parade.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I would put myself down as an oddity, a chapel man.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
